---
import PageLayout from "@/layouts/Base.astro";

const meta = {
	description: "About Lahcene - Software Engineer and Tech Enthusiast",
	title: "About",
};
---

<PageLayout meta={meta}>
	<h1 class="title mb-6">About Me</h1>
	<div class="prose prose-sm prose-cactus max-w-none">
		<p>
			Hello! I'm Lahcene, a passionate software engineer with a love for building elegant solutions to complex problems.
		</p>
		
		<h2>Professional Background</h2>
		<p>
			I specialize in full-stack development with a focus on creating responsive, user-friendly applications.
			Throughout my career, I've worked with various technologies and frameworks, always eager to learn and adapt to new challenges.
		</p>
		
		<h2>Skills & Expertise</h2>
		<ul class="list-inside list-disc" role="list">
			<li>Front-end development (HTML, CSS, JavaScript, React)</li>
			<li>Back-end development (Node.js, Python)</li>
			<li>Database design and management</li>
			<li>Cloud infrastructure (AWS, GCP)</li>
			<li>CI/CD and DevOps practices</li>
		</ul>
		
		<h2>Interests</h2>
		<p>
			Beyond coding, I'm interested in technology trends, open-source contributions, and the intersection of tech with other fields.
			When not in front of a computer, you might find me hiking, reading, or exploring new coffee shops.
		</p>
		
		<h2>This Blog</h2>
		<p>
			I created this blog to share my thoughts, experiences, and learnings in the world of software development and beyond.
			Expect articles about technical challenges I've overcome, useful tools I've discovered, and occasional reflections on the tech industry.
		</p>
		
		<p>
			Feel free to reach out if you'd like to discuss potential collaborations or just chat about technology!
		</p>
	</div>
</PageLayout>
